	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. D.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Accepi tuas illas breviculas, optime et charissime frater.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ex his intelligo te a <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l474" cert="high">Sangallo</placeName> et <placeName ref="l1976" cert="high">Augusta</placeName> accepisse <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1176" cert="high">Marsiliam</placeName> prope ereptam [regi] <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Galliarum</placeName> pontificis proditione.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Id san[e videtur ver]isimile, quod non ignorem pontificem [Romanum non] futurum pontificem, nisi talis sit prodit[or... sang]uinarius, parricida, turbator regn[orum omnium] atque verae religionis supplantator, idololatriae firmamentum; sed conteret ipsum brevi dominus.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l875" cert="high">Hispania</placeName> dudum habui herbescere ibi sementem evangelii et complures religionis syncerioris ergo misere trucidatos esse, sed nihilo minus augeri ecclesiam Christi, quae martyrum sanguine veluti letamine virescit et crescit.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nuper retulerunt <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l670" cert="high">Cathaloniam</placeName> et <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2749" cert="high">Aragoniam</placeName>, potentia <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l875" cert="high">Hispanica</placeName> regna, ultro a se abiecisse inquisitionem <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l875" cert="high">Hispanicam</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quod si verum est, brevi audiemus ampliora.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tam vero fidelis est <placeName type="auto_name">Guysianis</placeName> princeps <placeName ref="l572" cert="high">Wirtembergensis</placeName>, ut ad 16. martii <placeName ref="l1284" cert="high">Bruxellae</placeName> supra <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l471" cert="high">Spiram</placeName> comitia convocarit, nimirum sanguinariorum istorum caussam acturus fideliter.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Audio praeterea electorem <persName ref="p17927" cert="high">Palatinum</persName> eo vocatum, maxime ut expostuletur cum ipso admoneaturque serio, ut desinat esse sacramentarius et fovere <persName type="auto_name">Zvinglianos</persName>.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Man wirt den [guͦ]ten fürsten in die schuͦl fürren; wirt e[r...] dappffer sin und sich von denen fu[...], wirt er ein guͦte product haben un[d nit mi]serum pecus sin müssen und sagen zuͦ allem dem, das die groben schwermer (dann sy sind die rächten schwermer) singend und sagend: <foreign xml:lang="la">"Placet honorandi domini", cum digna supportatione etc.</foreign></s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Ich truwen gott, er werde schier den übermuͦt und stoltz demmen.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Comitia nunc celebrantur <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2" cert="high">Aaroviae</placeName> a 4 urbibus, Tiguro, <placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Berna</placeName>, <placeName ref="l28" cert="high">Basilea</placeName>, <placeName ref="l441" cert="high">Schaffhusia</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Legatus noster d. <persName type="auto_name">a Chaam</persName>, consul, hodie eo abivit.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Cumque <persName ref="p540" cert="high">Calvinus</persName> noster pridie datis ad me literis scripserit: "Cum superioribus diebus literas darem ad <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8055" cert="high">Ambrosium nostrum Blaurerum</persName>, nihil tibi scribere potui, nunc autem sarciam etc."</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Unde colligo te vel literas illas non accepisse adhuc vel te erga me non uti ea facilitate, qua ego erga te utor omnia communicando etc.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Fuerunt hic legati marchionissae <placeName type="auto_name">Neoburgensis</placeName> explicantes magistratui <placeName type="auto_name">Landarense</placeName> negotium.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tiguri, 23. martii 1562.</s>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Saluta fratres et amicos.</s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus ille.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo viro d. <persName ref="p8055" cert="high">Ambrosio Blaurero</persName>, civi <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l555" cert="high">Vitudurano</placeName>, et fideli servo Christi, domino colendo et fratri longe charissimo.</s>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l555" cert="high">Wintherdur</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
